folder: Oxford Street N. & Myrtle Avenue, Brooklyn, NY
original_title: Brooklyn: Oxford Street N. - Myrtle Avenue
text:
North Oxford Street, east side, north from Myrtle Avenue, seen from underneath the Myrtle Avenue elevated structure. The buildings seen in this view were later torn down to make way for the erection of Fort Greene Houses.

October 12, 1940

P. L. Sperr
